                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="team-card">
                        <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DonMassa84/Finca-BIO-MASSA/main/image/7.jpg" alt="Mme. Meyo Mefo Lydie" class="team-img">
